                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official record of this conversation has been found. The information set forth
                    above regarding the time of the meeting is taken from the President’s
                    appointment calendar, which gives the name only of Nelson. From Nelson, pp.
                    187–189, it appears, however, that the other persons listed above were also
                    present and that the principal subjects discussed were rubber and high-octane
                    gasoline.</p>
            </div>
